Author: Volentix_Official
Title: [BOUNTY] VOLENTIX | MULTI-PLATFORM ECOSYSTEM | 5 MILLION VTX | $500,000 | 🔴
Body: Volentix is one of the largest projects currently being undertaken by any crypto team, building one of the most innovative ecosystems (one of a handful to my knowledge), that will be near fully-functioning by mid 2019, shortly after our ICO ends. There's been over 2 years of development behind this project, and i do encourage you and everyone to have a look into our github, as it's getting updated daily by our developers. We'll keep pressing forward, no matter what.  The reputation of Volentix is very important. Recently several people have made comments that tokensuite has supported scam projects and that it is bad for Volentix to work together. We believe tokensuite is very successful in their business and very capable. Also Volentix is grateful to the people from tokensuite who have helped us.  We believe that tokensuite did not know if the projects they support are a scam or not. Perhaps, they should have checked more carefully but I do not believe tokensuite is directly a scam.  For the best of Volentix however, we decided to separate so Volentix may have its own reputation and for the public to judge the Volentix project based on its quality and not the history of the promoter.   As i copper member, i believe you should be able to join, as long as you're able to input the signatures that are on VENUE.   If there are any questions or comments in regards to the bounty stakes, please contact us and we'll resolve it asap.   About Volentix:  Github Whitepaper Greenpaper

Title: [BOUNTY] VOLENTIX | MULTI-PLATFORM ECOSYSTEM | 5 MILLION VTX | $500,000 | 🔴
Body: Bounty Has Ended on the 1st of January, 2019. Stay tuned for the next bounty starting Soon  Thank you for participating in the Volentix Bounty. The campaign has ended and stakes will be shared on our telegram channel t.me/VolentixBounty In order for all the participants to receive their stakes you must kindly follow the below instructions: ✅ Download the Verto Wallet Available for Mac and Windows Desktop only ➡️https://www.volentix.io/#downloadverto ✅ Must complete the whitelist application and verify your email https://Volentix.blocktopus.io/token_buyers/sign_up ✅ Associate your Verto wallet to your blocktopus account. Watch this video: ➡️https://youtu.be/E4oklGt98bU 🏧 How to Get VTX: ➡️https://youtu.be/xp9qvOCDAec     Official Volentix Bounty Program       Website   |   ANN   |   Twitter   |   Telegram   |   Github   |   Greenpaper            The Volentix Projectis a collaborative effort building software which enhances the use of cryptocurrency. The volentix ecosystem currently includes a decentralized cryptocurrency exchange which does not hold a user’s assets or personal information, a multi-currency crypto wallet, a cryptocurrency analytical engine with a ratings dashboard powered by artificial intelligence. Volentix is grown and powered by VTX tokens issued on the EOS blockchain and Volentix is still growing.  The Volentix Project already has many elements of decentralization and is already supported by several development teams and independent developers, all of whom are working independently, to reach complementary goals. This is what cryptocurrency is for, to unite a decentralized effort. The different parts of the Volentix ecosystem favor VTX tokens in some way. Tokenomics will always be cleverly structured to reward increasing the utility of VTX tokens.     Bounty Allocation  5,000,000 VTX Campaign ends February 1st, 2019. (3 months)      For Community Managers & Translation Bounties, visit this thread.        •   You must register on https://volentix.io/venue and subscribe to Volentix Mailing list.   •   ONLY DISCUSS BOUNTY-CAMPAIGNS IN VENUE TELEGRAM •   Bounty Campaign will end February 1st, 2019. •   Signature campaign does not work with “STAKES”, instead users earn VTX directly as a proportion related to the total number of users and total number of posts. •   VTX will be distributed  (30days after crowdsale is finished, Projected end date of Feb, 1st 2019) •   VTX earned will be calculated live but will change daily based on other users who are also posting and joining the signature campaign. Hint: To be successful post consistently and post high quality content. •   VTX earned during the bounty campaign will be credited to the participants’ VERTO WALLET (Volentix wallet) 30 days after close of crowdsale (30days after crowdsale is finished,     Projected end date of Feb, 1st 2019) •   Follower/Friend number cannot negatively/significantly change while campaign is running. •   Volentix reserves the right to eliminate you if it is thought that you have not been honest with your work. •   Volentix reserves the right to change bounty campaign rules, requirements, allocations and information at any time.  U.S and CHINESE RESIDENTS** are NOT allowed to partake in the bounty. KYC & AML CHECKS will be conducted for everyone, before you can claim your VTX tokens into your VERTO wallet.    DO NOT:  1.   Use multiple accounts. 2.   Cheat in any way. 3.   Use someone else to manage your participation. 4.   Use spamming or other mass marketing. 5.   Do any kind of unethical behavior when participating in any one of the campaigns, you will be disqualified from all bounties      Volentix Twitter  |  Twitter Sign-up  |  Spreadsheet   Rules  1.  You must register on https://volentix.io/venue as a user and subscribe to Volentix Mailing list. 2.  ONLY DISCUSS BOUNTY-CAMPAIGNS IN VENUE TELEGRAM 3.  All participants must follow our official twitter account to be eligible for the Twitter campaign 4.  Your audit score must be more than 90% according to https://www.twitteraudit.com. 5.  Your Twitter account must be mainly about cryptocurrency, blockchain, or decentralization/DAOs and have a minimum of 250 real followers or you must have more than 1000 real  followers without any content restriction in order to qualify. 6.  All participants will need to report their retweets and likes every single week in order to qualify. 7.  Please edit your first report to include your subsequent reports. Do not create new posts for new weeks; they may not be counted.   Task & Stakes  A minimum of 3 retweets. 1 Stake Per/Week A minimum of 3 likes. 1 Stake Per/Week    Please Authenticate Twitter Bounties in the Thread:           Volentix Telegram  |  Telegram Sign-up  | Spreadsheet   Rules  1.   You must register on https://volentix.io/venue as a user and subscribe to Volentix Mailing list. 2.  ONLY DISCUSS BOUNTY-CAMPAIGNS IN VENUE TELEGRAM 3.  Do not discuss bounties in official Volentix telegram channel 4.  Add Volentix.io to your telegram name   Task & Stakes  Join Volentix telegram and stay until the day of distribution (30days after crowdsale is finished) – 1 Stake EXTRA STAKES - Ask a question (NOT ABOUT BOUNTY) in the Volentix telegram t.me/volentix which creates discussion or invite lots of your friends to the Volentix telegram. Moderators may give you extra stakes. READ WHITE PAPER FOR DISCUSSION TOPICS.   Please Authenticate The Telegram Bounty in the Thread:   DATE Joined: (17/10/2018)  Telegram Authentication:  VENUE Name: XXXXX Telegram Name: @XXXX         Content Creation Sign-up  |  Spreadsheet   Rules  1.  You must register on https://volentix.io/venue as a user and subscribe to Volentix Mailing list. 2.  ONLY DISCUSS BOUNTY-CAMPAIGNS IN VENUE TELEGRAM 3.  You must have at least 100 organic subscribers on YouTube to participate. 4.  YouTube video must be at least 2 minutes long and the video should be descriptive. 5.  Speech must be made by a real person. 6.  Video has to be of good quality. 7.  The website / blog where you post content must be at least 3 months old. 8.  Your Medium/Steem.it/Youtube or any other free blogging blog page should have at least 100 followers. 9.  Your article / blog post / video must be public. Content at websites and blogs where the number of views is not transparent will not be accepted(Blogspot, Wordpress, etc.) 10.  Your written article / blog post has to be original, of good writing quality, and at least 500 words. 11.  Your article / blog post / video should have links to the our website and white paper. 12.  If you are submitting a website, it should have verifiable traffic. 13.  The same content can only be posted once. 14.  Applicant must indicate proof (bitcointalk profile, link, etc.) under the video or article she/he sends. 15.  Only original work is accepted, copying parts of the website / paper or using the work of someone else will disqualify your submission. 16.  Content on websites that do not appear in “Similarweb” analysis will not be accepted. 17.  Rules are strict to make sure Volentix’ reward quality submissions only and to make it fair for everyone. 18.  Each accepted submission will be carefully reviewed for acceptance. 19.  You will get proportional stakes based on the quality and popularity of your work, this will be subjectively reviewed at the end of the campaign. 20.  Stakes are based on the quality and popularity of the posted content. 21.  Articles/videos etc. will be evaluated according to the number of views and visitors and in terms of quality. 22.  Publications that are very influential and very good quality compared to others may be additionally rewarded with extra stakes. 23.  Content that does not satisfy any of the rules will not be accepted.   Task & Stakes  You will be able to get 1, 3, 5, 7, or 10 stake(s) depending on the number of visitors/ views/ similar-web points, and you will be able to get 1, 3, 5, 7, or 10 stake(s) depending on the content quality.           Note: the signature campaign is not managed on Bitcointalk, but on the Volentix bounty platform, Venue.   Rules  1.  You must register on https://volentix.io/venue as a user and subscribe to Volentix Mailing list. 2.  Signature Campaign registration occurs on venue.volentix.io, sign-up there and follow the instructions. 3.  ALL SIGNATURES ARE ON VENUE.VOLENTIX.IO 4.  Participants must be at least a Member or above on bitcointalk.org. If you are not at least a full member, you may participate in other campaigns, simply the signature campaign is not allowed. 5.  If you are found to be using multiple accounts, you will be banned. 6.  Spam and burst posts are not allowed. 7.  Volentix’ expect you to post constructive posts only. 8.  Some posts may be in local boards. 9.  Posts should not be made in bounties section, should not be off topic, archival, meta and politic sections. 10.  You will have to keep wearing the Volentix signature until the end of the campaign. 11.  All posts by all participants will be reviewed for integrity and quality. 12.  Your previous posts will be reviewed as well to see if your history is positive. 13.  If your rank changes during the campaign, please use issue form to notify a Bounty-Manager. 14.  Accounts with negative trust from DT-2 or DR-1 are not allowed to enroll.   Task & Stakes  Make at least 5 posts per week (75 characters minimum), within the alternative coin section (anywhere dealing with alt-coins). Sign-up on venue.volentix.io and follow the instructions.   • Member - 1 Stake Per/Week • Full-Member - 2 Stake Per/Week • Sr. Member - 3 Stakes Per/Week • Hero Member - 4 Stakes Per/Week • Legendary Member - 5 Stakes Per/Week        Need Assistance? & Bug/Tech Bounty   For all Technical Difficulties and Bug Bounties, Please fill out this form: https://goo.gl/4S7Tw6 We'll award you some VTX for your efforts!  You can view your submission post here.   If you have any questions, comments or concerns, please let us know. We'll assist you as soon as possible! We have a list of updates, and Q&A responses in the next post below.

Author: Volentix_Official
Title: [BOUNTY] VOLENTIX | MULTI-PLATFORM ECOSYSTEM | 5 MILLION VTX | $500,000 | 🔴
Body: Bounty Campaign Update (10/18/2018):  The Volentix team is working diligently behind the scenes, in order to meet our deadlines, and release our platforms according to our schedule. As we continue to move at a high velocity, we’ve decided to ultimately extend the bounty campaign until February 1st, 2019. During that time, our VERTO Multi-currency wallet will be up-and-running. By March 1st, 2019, you’ll have VTX coins in your wallet. This will have virtually no effect on how many coins you earn throughout the campaign, as stakes will be calculated on a basis to award users the highest amount, allocating and distributing the proper amount of VTX to every individual.  All current bounty stakes have been calculated, and are available to view on the various of spreadsheets. The associated values in VTX, will not be fully public until Feb 1st, 2019, when the bounty campaign ends. If you have any questions in regards to your current earned stakes, or any issues, please contact us ASAP on our telegram channel. The bounty spreadsheet and the form of registrations will remain unchanged. By initiating an extension to our campaign, there will be a consolidation of all your stakes, effectively we’ll begin the campaign from “Week 1.”  If you’ve already applied to the bounty campaign, please resume operations as normal. Again, all your information and details are secured, we’ve taken a snapshot of everyone’s participation up this point. And we want to iterate again, the current “weeks” you’ve been keeping a record of will reset, you will start from Week 1 starting October 17th. Please update your Bitcointalk posts ASAP.  If you have any further questions, comments or concerns, please feel free to let us know on our Telegram, and we’ll get in-touch with you as soon as possible.  Thank you for your participation,  ~Volentix Team     Frequently Asked Questions   I hope all is well with this project. First it was BountySuite relinquishing the management of this bounty, now there's a reset more like, and bounty is extending to February 2019. What are the guarantees this won't be waste of time??  Volentix is one of the largest projects currently being undertaken by any crypto team, building one of the most innovative ecosystems (one of a handful to my knowledge), that will be near fully-functioning by mid 2019, shortly after our ICO ends. There's been over 2 years of development behind this project, and i do encourage you and everyone to have a look into our github, as it's getting updated daily by our developers. We'll keep pressing forward, no matter what.  The reputation of Volentix is very important. Recently several people have made comments that tokensuite has supported scam projects and that it is bad for Volentix to work together. We believe tokensuite is very successful in their business and very capable. Also Volentix is grateful to the people from tokensuite who have helped us.  We believe that tokensuite did not know if the projects they support are a scam or not. Perhaps, they should have checked more carefully but I do not believe tokensuite is directly a scam.  For the best of Volentix however, we decided to separate so Volentix may have its own reputation and for the public to judge the Volentix project based on its quality and not the history of the promoter.   Where can i learn more about Volentix?  Here are some reading materials, and daily activity on our Github:  More About Volentix:  Github Whitepaper Greenpaper
